 *     iterator} divided into partitions
 * @throws IllegalArgumentException if {@code size} is nonpositive
 */
""";

        String[] parameters = Arrays.stream(javadoc.split("\n"))
                .filter(line -> line.contains("@param") || line.contains("@return"))
                .skip(1)
                .map(line -> {
